		<description><html:strong>For example:</html:strong> given the <html:strong>&quot;[b]%insert_selection_anchor_here%[/b]&quot;</html:strong> snippet, and some selected text in the current page, the <html:strong>&quot;[b]&quot;</html:strong> part of the snippet will be inserted at the <html:strong>beginning</html:strong> of the selection and the <html:strong>&quot;[/b]&quot;</html:strong> part of the snippet will be inserted at the <html:strong>end</html:strong> of the selection.</description>
	</tooltip>
